In order to make a executable program we have to make a directory and then make a file with the program, this can be achieved by following commands:

debian@beaglebone:~$ mkdir qtproject
debian@beaglebone:~$ cd qtproject

debian@beaglebone:~/qtproject$ nano example.cpp


Program for exapmle.cpp
#include <QApplication>
#include <QLabel>
int main(int argc, char *argv[ ]){

 QApplication app(argc, argv);
 QLabel label("Hello World!");
 	label.resize(200, 100);
 	label.show();
 	return app.exec();
}
